room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped" by Escape Port Charlotte in Fort Myers
room_address: 3191 Harbor Blvd Unit C Port Charlotte, FL 33952
room_description:
Some time ago, there were a string of kidnappings in your area. There were many theories about the identity of the captor, but no arrest was ever made. One day, the kidnappings stopped abruptly. Over time, people started using the stories to keep children from roaming the streets at night, suggesting the people were taken and eaten alive.
You and your friends go to investigate the old stories. You hear muffled talking and then the door slams. Can you escape before the kidnappersâ€™ return?
